<h3 class="hp-section-sub-header">
Информация о компании
</h3>
<p data-ga-id="host">On addition to the THE Hotel&#39;s short term room availability, it offers more. 
THE Hotel Finland Oy est. 2019 offers accommodation for long term guests such as project workers and for those, working away-from-home. The types of property available are approximately, 50 rooms at THE Hotel in Hamina and also apartments and terraced houses else where in Hamina-Kotka region. 
Cost affective and compatible price range to suit all budgets and companies requirements. More details on request!</p>
<h3 class="hp-section-sub-header">
Информация об объекте размещения
</h3>
<p data-ga-id="property">THE Hotel is recently renovated former police station and courthouse in Hamina. Modern and relaxed style rooms are suitable for those looking for both short and long-term accommodation. THE Hotel is centrally located on the Town Hall Square and offers:
• En-suite single and double&#47;twin rooms with TV
• Single rooms with shared bathroom facilities
• Rooms have an electric kettle
• Shared kitchen, lounge area and bathroom facilities for the
long-stay guests.
• The Bar &amp; lounge has a two table poolroom (due to open in September 2021)
• Use of sauna on request</p>
<h3 class="hp-section-sub-header">
Информация о районе
</h3>
<p data-ga-id="neighbourhood">Fortress Trail
Did you know that you can experience the calming peace of nature right in the centre of Hamina? The 4.5-kilometres Fortress Trail meanders in the fortress ramparts in Hamina. You can walk an almost complete circle along the ramparts surrounding the centre of Hamina.
You get to walk over exciting vaulted corridors, beside built bulwarks and past the renovated Hamina Bastion with its casemate vaults. The trail also offers views of the magnificent old buildings of Hamina.
What else is in Hamina?
Museum Ships
Public beaches
Archipelago
Churches and cemeteries
Historic sites
Flag World
Nature trails
Museums
Statues and monuments, and much more.</p>
